in this code, i notice the filter part is too hard-coded, also not able to work with QueryTable

enums. Here's a modified version that should work:

```python
class QueryTable(str, Enum):
    case = "Case"
    case_status = "CaseStatus"
    leads = "Leads"
    lead_type = "LeadType"
    rebate_record = "RebateRecord"

table_models = {
    QueryTable.case: Case,
    QueryTable.case_status: CaseStatus,
    QueryTable.leads: Leads,
    QueryTable.lead_type: LeadType,
    QueryTable.rebate_record: RebateRecord,
}

@api_router.post("/filter")
def table_keyword_filter(table: QueryTable, query: str, db: Session = Depends(get_db)):
    table_class = table_models[table]
    q = db.query(table_class)
    if table == QueryTable.case:
        q = q.filter(or_(
            Case.customer_name.like(f"%{query}%"),
            Case.address.like(f"%{query}%"),
            func.cast(Case.customer_contact_number, String).like(f"%{query}%"),
            func.cast(Case.customer_phone_number, String).like(f"%{query}%"),
        ))
    elif table == QueryTable.case_status:
        q = q.filter(CaseStatus.code.like(f"%{query}%"))
    elif table == QueryTable.leads:
        q = q.filter(or_(
            Leads.customer_name.like(f"%{query}%"),
            func.cast(Leads.customer_phone, String).like(f"%{query}%"),
            func.cast(Leads.customer_contact_phone, String).like(f"%{query}%"),
        ))
    elif table == QueryTable.lead_type:
        q = q.filter(LeadType.name.like(f"%{query}%"))
    elif table == QueryTable.rebate_record:
        q = q.filter(or_(
            RebateRecord.handler.like(f"%{query}%"),
            RebateRecord.borrower_name.like(f"%{query}%"),
            RebateRecord.mortgage_address.like(f"%{query}%"),
        ))
    else:
        # handle unknown table types
        return []
    return q.all()
```

This version first creates a dictionary mapping the `QueryTable` enum values to their corresponding model objects. It then uses this dictionary to dynamically select the appropriate model class to use in the query.

The filter part is now split into separate cases for each table type. For each case, only the relevant fields are filtered and the query is built accordingly. This approach should be more modular and easier to modify if you need to add additional table types or fields to search on.

在使用Aspose.Words来读取Word文件中的文字之前，需要安装Aspose.Words for .NET NuGet包。安装完成之后，可以使用以下代码示例读取Word文件中的文字：

```
// 加载Word文档
Document doc = new Document("input.docx");

// 提取文本
string text = doc.GetText();

// 打印文本内容
Console.WriteLine(text);
